## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

Built with **Domain-Driven Design** and **Clean Architecture**:

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ domain/                 # Business Logic Layer
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ entities/          # Contact, Note, Tag
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ value_objects/     # Phone, Email, Birthday, Address
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ validators/        # Data validation rules
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ application/           # Application Layer
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ services/         # ContactService, NoteService
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ commands/         # Command handlers
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ infrastructure/        # Infrastructure Layer
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ storage/          # SQLite, JSON, Pickle
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ persistence/      # Data access
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ serialization/    # Data serialization
‚îÇ
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ presentation/         # Presentation Layer
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cli/             # Command-line interface
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ nlp/             # NLP pipeline (ML models)
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ web/             # MCP server

tests/                    # 500+ tests, 97% coverage
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ unit/                # Unit tests
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ integration/         # Integration tests
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ performance/         # Performance tests
```

### Design Principles

- ‚úÖ **SOLID principles**
- ‚úÖ **Dependency Inversion**
- ‚úÖ **Separation of Concerns**
- ‚úÖ **Type Safety** (100% type hints)
- ‚úÖ **Testability** (97% coverage)

